{"tid":717392,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個住airbnb嘅難忘經歷","createTime":"2018-06-26T04:02:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T11:28:32.000Z","uid":132750,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"77debe2c98938a75783961d9826c7243140faee7","tid":717392,"uid":132750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:02:36.000Z","msg":"去沖繩住間airbnb 明明睇相好光鮮<br />\n評價都唔差<br />\n<br />\n點知一入屋d裝修勁霉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n張床嘅床單係深色 一睇就睇得出無換過<br />\n個下都已經屌咗出聲<br />\n到第二晚仲見到有隻大曱甴係屋入面<br />\n<br />\n以後唔會再住airbnb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e184e598028e0acd25d6483cc8f7d46fb5a4ad62","tid":717392,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:07:17.000Z","msg":"有冇睇評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b92324e6f9919849cd6c24ed4b3c7df8e9f5263","tid":717392,"uid":33975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:14:11.000Z","msg":"有冇 link ?"},{"pid":"dd911dd6fc78be6f2691a9f216dfb2e6b098686e","tid":717392,"uid":162194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:24:50.000Z","msg":"舊年暑假去東京，間屋有2間房4張床<br />\n點知去到發現其中一間房鎖咗<br />\n研究咗好撚耐點開<br />\n後尾自己用個銀仔扭開咗<br />\n入到去發現有張床係爛嘅<br />\n有個角落頭凹咗一大忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而無鎖個間房都有一張床係爛嘅<br />\n凹撚咗去中間"},{"pid":"8bf3ae207deb7db30abc293f06b505147a6e4c9c","tid":717392,"uid":162194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:26:25.000Z","msg":"有一次去布吉<br />\n間屋係4樓(最高層)<br />\n屌你老母日日都唔夠水沖涼<br />\n一時大一時細<br />\n朋友沖沖下得返一滴水"},{"pid":"82e24fea227e39bb8d00d80c38ff34348e1b6d6f","tid":717392,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"有次喺大阪，房主架妹被分手回家；扮關心嘅我問候下幾句飲下酒咁。事發突發，就咁中出咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e44ee043c801b7284babf897c781abbeedbd953","tid":717392,"uid":61766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:09:52.000Z","msg":"冬天去巴黎負幾度<br />\n個host 失蹤揾唔到佢<br />\n企左半個鐘凍到媽媽聲<br />\n咁就去食個飯先<br />\n食左無耐<br />\n佢打比我鬧我點解唔企係度等佢<br />\n仲要限我十分鐘內見人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nOn99"},{"pid":"265182192da243d95ca65505ebba70026c0f8195","tid":717392,"uid":162194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"有次去巴黎 淨係租咗間房<br />\n屋主係一對情侶<br />\n晨早流流係到啪啪啪<br />\n嘈鬼住曬"},{"pid":"53a8b5cdc0cf18bb6f60c2cc396f3e1b685278ac","tid":717392,"uid":132750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"所以住宿呢d真係無得貪平 <br />\n平野無好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76fd6cd4a323665f0aa474a677f903a575e4c37","tid":717392,"uid":591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T11:28:32.000Z","msg":"住過一次東京bnb<br />\n唔想再住多次 寧願住酒店<br />\n一入屋有陣嗡味<br />\n張床單有漬<br />\n地下多塵<br />\n試過有晚無啦啦跳制<br />\n全屋無電"}]}